# Styling & UI Component Rules

## Tailwind CSS

- **Framework**: Tailwind CSS v4 with PostCSS
- **Config**: [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js) and [prettier.config.js](mdc:prettier.config.js)
- **Global Styles**: [src/styles/globals.css](mdc:src/styles/globals.css)
- **Theme**: Teal color scheme (`teal-500`, `teal-50`)

## Component Library

Reusable components in [src/components/](mdc:src/components/):

- **Button**: [src/components/Button/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/Button/index.tsx)
- **TextInput**: [src/components/TextInput/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/TextInput/index.tsx)
- **Textarea**: [src/components/Textarea/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/Textarea/index.tsx)
- **SelectInput**: [src/components/SelectInput/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/SelectInput/index.tsx)
- **MultipleSelectChips**: [src/components/MultipleSelectChips/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/MultipleSelectChips/index.tsx)

## UI Patterns

- **Form Layout**: Use `space-y-6` for form sections
- **Centered Content**: `mx-auto max-w-3xl` for main content width
- **Icons**: Use Lucide React icons with consistent sizing
- **Cards**: Use rounded borders and proper spacing
- **Colors**: Stick to the teal theme with gray text hierarchy

## Component Structure

```tsx
// Standard component structure
const ComponentName = ({ prop1, prop2 }: Props) => {
  return (
    <div className="space-y-6">
      <div className="text-center">{/* Header with icon */}</div>
      <div className="space-y-6">{/* Form fields */}</div>
    </div>
  )
}
```

## Responsive Design

- Mobile-first approach with Tailwind responsive prefixes
- Use `max-w-3xl` for content containers
- Ensure touch-friendly button sizes (min 44px)
- Test on mobile devices for travel app usage

## Accessibility

- Use proper semantic HTML elements
- Include `aria-label` for icon buttons
- Ensure proper color contrast ratios
- Use focus states for keyboard navigation
